												<div class="description author withsidebar">
													<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/michaelkraus/">Michael Kraus</a></h6>
													Michael Kraus is a Los Angeles-based screenwriter who has written for TNT’s Snowpiercer. His essays about movies and television appear in Lit Hub and CrimeReads.																									</div>
